mods.abstract: Three color window card (navy, blue - green and gray on white) announcing the Nashville Predators 2009-2010 season with Predators versus Detroit, St. Louis, Columbus, and Chicago. Poster features a woodcut of the Nashville skyline. Poster is a limited edition of 100, series 7.
